text:
(MENAFN Press) Authentic-Online-Ivf-Pharmacy Oct. 12 2015 - PRLog -- As the leading online pharmacy IVFPrescriptions understands the importance of maintaining transparency and a positive image with potential customers. For this reason we are the only online pharmacy that has customer service attendants available via phone or e-mail 7 days per week to answer your questions about the medications were offer the ordering process and how we work.Our website is trusted by doctors clinics and patients around the world to deliver brand name IVF medications. We are an approved pharmacy that can only sell medications with a valid prescription from a doctor. We have pharmacies in Tel Aviv London and Hamburg and deliver medications worldwide.Our goal is to eliminate any perceived risk you might have in ordering IVF meds online. Through transparency careful handling of your brand name medications and exceptional customer service we ensure you get the medications you need when you need them from an approved pharmacy.If you ever have any questions about the medications we offer our qualifications or the ordering process do not hesitate to contact us at or call us at 866-989-0078. Customer service representatives are available by the phone seven days a week from 8AM to 10PM EST.For More Details: http://ivfprescriptions.com/ Contactivfprescriptions***omkarlabs.com--- End ---
